# ============================================================================
# TROUBLESHOOTING & TESTING
# ============================================================================
#
# 1. Verify data ingestion:
#    index=azure sourcetype="azure:aad:signin" | head 10
#    index=azure sourcetype="azure:aad:audit" | head 10
#    index=azure sourcetype="azure:aad:riskdetection" | head 10
#
# 2. Test with shorter timeframe:
#    Replace earliest=-7d with earliest=-1h for faster testing
#
# 3. Check field extractions:
#    | table UserPrincipalName, IPAddress, ResultType, RiskLevelDuringSignIn
#
# 4. Validate join operations:
#    Test each subsearch independently before joining
#
# 5. Performance tuning:
#    - Use summary indexing for large datasets
#    - Enable data model acceleration
#    - Adjust time ranges based on data volume
# ============================================================================
